    {
      "id": "detailed_2_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and serves as a reliable daily driver, though it shows clear signs of its age. The engine and transmission are functional, but you may notice some typical wear such as minor oil seepage and a slightly aged suspension feel. The exterior has several noticeable scratches and some paint fading on the roof, while the interior shows significant wear on the driver's seat and some cracked plastic trim. All essential electronics work, but the air conditioning takes a moment to get cold and the infotainment screen has a few dead pixels. It\u2019s a solid choice for someone looking for a dependable workhorse who doesn't mind a bit of cosmetic character.",
      "price": 23000.0,
      "reputation": 0.9,
