      "timestep_posted": 15
    },
    {
      "id": "optimistic_5_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_5",
      "description": "Experience the gold standard with this absolute stunner! This car is in pristine, mint condition, looking and driving exactly like it just rolled off the showroom floor. From its flawless exterior to the immaculate, fresh-smelling interior, every detail has been perfectly preserved. It\u2019s a rare opportunity to own a vehicle that truly feels brand new\u2014don't miss out on this incredible find!",
